{"title":"Saris SuperClamp Gets Modern Makeover, New Freedom is Most Compact Tray-Style Hitch Rack","link":"https://bikerumor.com/saris-unveils-two-all-new-redesigned-hitch-racks-freedom-superclamp/","date":1745867773000,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Saris-freedom-rack--1536x864.webp\" width=\"1536\" height=\"864\" alt=\"Saris freedom rack\" /></p>\n<p>We got our hands on the latest hitch rack lineup from Saris while at Sea Otter Classic, and they look built for battle. From everyday utility to full-blown e-bike hauling, Saris has an all-new trio of racks built around modern bikes and modern needs, which could put them back at the forefront of the bike rack space. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>The recently launched Saris Edge (<a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/saris-gains-an-edge-with-new-premium-hitch-bike-rack/\">Check out Jeremy’s review here</a>) is leading the charge, a premium rack designed to meet the growing demands of e-bike transport. The new Edge is backed by two fresh takes on Saris’ most-loved models: the Freedom (Made in the USA) and SuperClamp (Built for the longer haul).</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Saris-Superclamp-rack-scaled.webp\"><img width=\"2560\" height=\"1920\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Saris-Superclamp-rack-scaled.webp\" alt=\"Saris Superclamp rack\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Saris-Superclamp-rack-scaled.webp 2560w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Saris-Superclamp-rack-297x223.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Saris-Superclamp-rack-1536x1152.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Saris-Superclamp-rack-120x90.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Saris-Superclamp-rack-768x576.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Saris-Superclamp-rack-2048x1536.webp 2048w\" /></a><figcaption>(Photos: Jordan Villella/BikeRumor.com)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Saris SuperClamp – Speedy Loading, Sleek Footprint</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The updated SuperClamp is all about fast loading, tight security, and minimal fuss. With a spring-loaded arm that locks down without touching the frame, it is a favorite among folks who transport carbon bikes or want to avoid frame rub.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Saris-Superclamp-rack-pull--scaled.webp\"><img width=\"1536\" height=\"864\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Saris-Superclamp-rack-pull--1536x864.webp\" alt=\"Saris Superclamp rack pull\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Saris-Superclamp-rack-pull--1536x864.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Saris-Superclamp-rack-pull--297x167.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Saris-Superclamp-rack-pull--120x68.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Saris-Superclamp-rack-pull--768x432.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Saris-Superclamp-rack-pull--2048x1152.webp 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Saris-Superclamp-rack-pull--1200x675.webp 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Saris-Superclamp-rack-clamp--scaled.webp\"><img width=\"1536\" height=\"1152\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Saris-Superclamp-rack-clamp--1536x1152.webp\" alt=\"Saris Superclamp rack clamp\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Saris-Superclamp-rack-clamp--1536x1152.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Saris-Superclamp-rack-clamp--297x223.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Saris-Superclamp-rack-clamp--120x90.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Saris-Superclamp-rack-clamp--768x576.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Saris-Superclamp-rack-clamp--2048x1536.webp 2048w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Saris-Superclamp-rack-wheel--scaled.webp\"><img width=\"1536\" height=\"864\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Saris-Superclamp-rack-wheel--1536x864.webp\" alt=\"Saris Superclamp rack wheel\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Saris-Superclamp-rack-wheel--1536x864.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Saris-Superclamp-rack-wheel--297x167.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Saris-Superclamp-rack-wheel--120x68.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Saris-Superclamp-rack-wheel--768x432.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Saris-Superclamp-rack-wheel--2048x1152.webp 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Saris-Superclamp-rack-wheel--1200x675.webp 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The new version includes tool-free anti-wobble technology, a welcome addition that keeps things rock-solid without the need for a toolbox. Saris also added a folding and tilting mechanism, which makes storage and access that much easier. It still handles bikes up to 60 lbs. each, so yes, your e-bike is good to go here, too. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Saris still has the SuperClamp G3 rack on the website in both 2 and 4 bike versions, so it’s not clear yet if this will replace the current SuperClamp, or just add to the existing lineup. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>SuperClamp Key Features</strong>:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Zero Frame Contact</strong> – Spring-loaded arm secures bikes by the wheels, not the frame.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>All-Aluminum Construction</strong> – Lightweight, rust-resistant, and durable.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Tool-Free Anti-Wobble System</strong> – Rock-solid fit without needing tools.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Adjustable Front Wheel Block</strong> – Fits wheels from 20″ to 29″.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Folding &amp; Tilting</strong> – For compact storage and rear trunk access.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><span><strong>E-Bike Friendly</strong> – Supports two bikes up to 60 lbs. each.</span></li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>MSRP</strong>: $799.99</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Saris-Freedom-with-rack-1.webp\"><img width=\"2030\" height=\"1174\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Saris-Freedom-with-rack-1.webp\" alt=\"Saris Freedom bike rack\n\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Saris-Freedom-with-rack-1.webp 2030w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Saris-Freedom-with-rack-1-297x172.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Saris-Freedom-with-rack-1-1536x888.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Saris-Freedom-with-rack-1-120x69.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Saris-Freedom-with-rack-1-768x444.webp 768w\" /></a><figcaption>(Photo/Saris)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Saris Freedom – Light, Compact, and Built in the USA</strong></h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The Freedom Rack lives up to its name. Made entirely in the USA, it’s the lightest and most compact two-bike tray-style rack in Saris’ lineup. Thanks to a fixed-position arm, it is designed with zero frame contact, giving peace of mind whether you’re hauling a steel gravel bike or an ultralight carbon race rig.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Saris-freedom-rack--scaled.webp\"><img width=\"1536\" height=\"864\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Saris-freedom-rack--1536x864.webp\" alt=\"Saris freedom rack\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Saris-freedom-rack--1536x864.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Saris-freedom-rack--297x167.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Saris-freedom-rack--120x68.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Saris-freedom-rack--768x432.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Saris-freedom-rack--2048x1152.webp 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Saris-freedom-rack--1200x675.webp 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Saris-freedom--scaled.webp\"><img width=\"1536\" height=\"864\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Saris-freedom--1536x864.webp\" alt=\"Saris freedom\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Saris-freedom--1536x864.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Saris-freedom--297x167.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Saris-freedom--120x68.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Saris-freedom--768x432.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Saris-freedom--2048x1152.webp 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Saris-freedom--1200x675.webp 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Saris-Superclamp-rack-top-clamp--scaled.webp\"><img width=\"1536\" height=\"864\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Saris-Superclamp-rack-top-clamp--1536x864.webp\" alt=\"Saris Superclamp rack top clamp\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Saris-Superclamp-rack-top-clamp--1536x864.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Saris-Superclamp-rack-top-clamp--297x167.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Saris-Superclamp-rack-top-clamp--120x68.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Saris-Superclamp-rack-top-clamp--768x432.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Saris-Superclamp-rack-top-clamp--2048x1152.webp 2048w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/Saris-Superclamp-rack-top-clamp--1200x675.webp 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>We especially liked the Fast Fit Technology—a rotating wheel tray that automatically adjusts to different wheelbases without requiring extra fiddling. Add an anti-wobble hitch pin and rust-resistant aluminum construction, and you have a rack that exceeds its price point. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Saris Freedom Key Features</strong>:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Aluminum Construction</strong> – Lightweight, strong, and corrosion-resistant.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Fixed Position Arm</strong> – Secures bikes without contacting the frame or fork.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Fast Fit Technology</strong> – Wheel tray auto-adjusts for different wheelbases.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Anti-Wobble System</strong> – The locking hitch pin ensures stability on rough roads.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Compact Design</strong> – The smallest footprint of any 2-bike tray-style rack.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>MSRP</strong>: $499.99</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Look for more details on both these new racks coming soon!</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://saris.com/collections/hitch-racks\">Saris.com</a></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/saris-unveils-two-all-new-redesigned-hitch-racks-freedom-superclamp/\">Saris SuperClamp Gets Modern Makeover, New Freedom is Most Compact Tray-Style Hitch Rack</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Jordan Villella","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"bcc9775dbf4e3140440b47e07e5ceda37e0372031ebb58aaab69a28e31367755","category":"Cycling"}